The desire of death cannot be satisfied,<lb/>
                  <pb n="4"/>
                 <lb/>
                  <quote type="biblical" ana="Hab 2.5">he <normalised orig="gathereth" auto="true">gathers</normalised> <normalised orig="vnto" auto="true">unto</normalised> <normalised orig="himselfe" auto="true">himself</normalised> all nations,<lb/>
