                  <head>The second reason why all men must die,</head>
<p>Is <normalised orig="drawne" auto="true">drawn</normalised> from the <normalised orig="vprightnesse" auto="true">uprightness</normalised> of<lb/>
Gods <normalised orig="iustice" auto="true">justice</normalised>. <normalised orig="Sinne" auto="true">Sin</normalised> being so <normalised orig="generall" auto="true">general</normalised> in<lb/>
all men, his <normalised orig="Maiestie" auto="true">Majesty</normalised> <normalised orig="hath" auto="true">has</normalised> decreed to<lb/>
