<normalised orig="owne" auto="true">own</normalised> <normalised orig="deare" auto="true">dear</normalised> children; who although<lb/>
the guilt of <normalised orig="sinne" auto="true">sin</normalised> be <normalised orig="remoued" auto="true">removed</normalised> and taken<lb/>
