so <normalised orig="subiect" auto="true">subject</normalised> to <normalised orig="sinne" auto="true">sin</normalised>. Saint Paul said,<lb/>
                  <quote type="biblical" ana="Rom 5.12">Death went <normalised orig="ouer" auto="true">over</normalised> all men, in as much as<lb/>
