                  <pb n="8"/>
            <div>
                  <head>The third reason why all men 
must die.</head>
<p>All men must die in respect of Gods<lb/>
<normalised orig="generall" auto="true">general</normalised> purpose for the changing and<lb/>
renewing of mankind from one substance<lb/>
into another, for the <normalised orig="transubsta~tiating" auto="false">transsubstantiating</normalised><lb/>
of one body into another, &amp;<lb/>
